{"tid":2060764,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"窮閪入娛樂圈？戴祖儀百萬掃玩具等升值","createTime":"2020-06-12T01:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T10:06:50.000Z","uid":213877,"like":3,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c728a4f5eed43e44e5cc1317f38d8234897f6c5c","tid":2060764,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:35:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001.html&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0rXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=bd11ef78\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=f52dc3bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家有富爸爸玩另類投資！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=ad336a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塗鴉大師KAWS公仔，相信大家都唔陌生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=2c160fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n要數最揼本之作，祖儀首推這幅畫作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_04p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=1d0e38c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成櫃玩具模型，恨死有收藏此系列的同好！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_05p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=9c2b5de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴祖儀曾在直播公開用作存放收藏品的Studio。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_06p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=c435f4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBaldur Helgason作品數千美元購入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200612/photo/bkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_07p.jpg?20200612050625\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200612%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200612033017107-0612_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20200612050625&h=451091eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滑浪機器人（空山基）過萬元購入升值8倍。<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的「學霸女神」戴祖儀有腦又有樣，有家底的她拒靠富爸爸，憑新世代眼光投資百萬，短短3年狂掃近百件玩具藝術品，部分珍藏升值潛力達7、8倍！她坦言除非將來窮到燶，否則不捨得變賣家當。<br />\n<br />\n畢業於英國（萊斯特）大學名校法律系的星夢歌手戴祖儀，有位從事地產的富爸爸，她有律師不做，反而投身演藝界工作。年紀輕輕的她具投資頭腦及本錢，笑說：「我唔係投資股票、黃金、珠寶鑽石，呢啲入門價再高啲，我係另類投資！」<br />\n<br />\n原來祖儀早於3年前已開始投資自己喜愛的潮流藝術品及玩具品牌Hot Toys模型，近百件珍藏品有條理地分類存放在兩個Studio，據知總值過百萬！她透露玩具模型每款售價約2,000元，部分較多人搶購的限量版要預早落訂，否則就要「食」炒價：「以前升值得比較多，近年有回落迹象，頂多升值一至兩倍。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6位數買畫</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於其他潮流藝術品，價錢至少5位數，例如塗鴉大師KAWS的招牌XX公仔，有錢都未必買到，祖儀說：「要睇吓邊隻公仔，Classic多人搶嗰啲起碼要6位數，如果炒價細細隻嗰啲，5位數買到，都有升值潛力，最少多幾倍！」她亦擁有一個巨型村上隆多啦A夢藝術品，同樣價值不菲，至於空山基的機械人珍藏，她記得以過萬元買入，如今已升值8倍！眾多收藏品中，她笑言「課金」最多的，是去年底買入的Shepard Fairey一幅巨型畫作，價值達6位數！"},{"pid":"0371ebf98d85ffa54eb08c0b595d38a1eca59fdd","tid":2060764,"uid":213877,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"今時今日入得行做娛樂圈有幾個係窮屋企？"},{"pid":"6e649e594649fea0797ba5a7704fd25f2ac75636","tid":2060764,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:38:47.000Z","msg":"dllm成個櫃ht<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2977e2d421ad543fe9cc41ae3fda10ed6b62fabe","tid":2060764,"uid":32028,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"0371ebf98d85ffa54eb08c0b595d38a1eca59fdd","tid":2060764,"uid":213877,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"今時今日入得行做娛樂圈有幾個係窮屋企？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:41:52.000Z","msg":"老豆：搵份工做下啦，雖然老豆有錢，但都唔可以日日係屋企做廢人，你想做咩，同我講，我有既係錢<br />\n<br />\n阿女：想做明星"},{"pid":"ca3b742c45c1f78e9667ced328fcc5898e7fc804","tid":2060764,"uid":223084,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"對腳玩一晚要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce0ec00a4a9deef796bc005cda16056853ee478","tid":2060764,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2977e2d421ad543fe9cc41ae3fda10ed6b62fabe","tid":2060764,"uid":32028,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"0371ebf98d85ffa54eb08c0b595d38a1eca59fdd","tid":2060764,"uid":213877,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"今時今日入得行做娛樂圈有幾個係窮屋企？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:41:52.000Z","msg":"老豆：搵份工做下啦，雖然老豆有錢，但都唔可以日日係屋企做廢人，你想做咩，同我講，我有既係錢<br />\n<br />\n阿女：想做明星"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:43:21.000